  "title": "HOD - English Academic",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead and develop a team of teachers ensure high standards of teaching and learning</li>\n  <li>Oversee the curriculum development of a comprehensive, high-quality and cost-effective digital curriculum program, ensuring its alignment with industry standards and educational best practices.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the management team provide strategic curriculum framework and thorough regular reviews across all curriculum department</li>\n  <li>Update and evolve needs on syllabus changes, emerging trends to ensure its relevance and effectiveness</li>\n  <li>Role model for subject team to foster a professional educator development and maintain professional presence for the company</li>\n  <li>Provide feedback and support to subject team on regular performance review and facilitate their professional growth</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelors or Master Degree in Education or related fields</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years in leading a team of teachers in relevant subject curriculum</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years of teaching experience in relevant subject</li>\n  <li>Has strong subject-content teaching and able to develop curriculum support relevant academic for teaching</li>\n  <li>Excellent leadership skills</li>\n  <li>Have a positive mindset towards picking up new skills and knowledge</li>\n  <li>Must be bilingual able to communicate in English, Mandarin</li>\n</ul>",
